'''大衛·愛德華·艾加'''（{{lang-en|'''David Edward Edgar'''}}，{{IPAc-en|ˈ|ɛ|d|ɡ|ər}}，{{bd|1987年|5月19日|catIdx=Edgar, David}}）在[[加拿大|加拿大]][[安大略省|安大略省]][[基秦拿|基秦拿]]出生，是一名前[[足球|足球]][[運動員|運動員]]，場上司職[[後衛_(足球)#中後衛|中堅]]，亦可以擔任[[後衛_(足球)#邊後衛|左或右閘]]，出身[[纽卡斯尔联足球俱乐部|紐卡素]]青訓系統，曾效力[[哈特尔普尔联足球俱乐部|哈特尔普尔]]。

艾加曾代表加拿大參加各個年齡級別國際賽及[[加拿大国家男子足球队|加拿大]]大國腳。他以加拿大U20成員身份參加2007年世青盃，並於2011年2月9日首次為成年隊上陣。

== 生平 ==
=== 早年 ===
大卫·埃德加生於[[加拿大|加拿大]][[安大略省|安大略省]][[基秦拿|基秦拿]]，父親埃迪·埃德加亦是一名職業足球員，司職[[守門員_(足球)|門將]]，曾效力英格蘭的[[纽卡斯尔联足球俱乐部|纽卡斯尔联]]和[[哈特尔普尔联足球俱乐部|哈特尔普尔联]]，以及美國的[[紐約宇宙|紐約宇宙]]<ref name="Sports Express">{{cite web |url=http://www.sportsexpress.ca/soccer.htm#David%20Edgar%20plays%20with%20soccer%20Goliath%20Newcastle%20United |accessdate=3 January 2007 |title=David Edgar's the new kid on the block at Newcastle United |last=Palmer |first=Ian S. |newspaper=Sports Express |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070510203709/http://www.sportsexpress.ca/soccer.htm#David%20Edgar%20plays%20with%20soccer%20Goliath%20Newcastle%20United |archivedate=2007-05-10 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。大卫·埃德加自小便十分鐘愛體育，曾參與[[冰球|冰球]]、中長跑和足球<ref name="Sports Express" />。

當艾加9歲時，他的父親帶他到英格蘭參加一項由曼聯贊助的足球競賽，賽事中艾加表現出色，曼聯有意提供獎學金讓他接受青訓，但艾加婉拒，寧願返回加拿大繼續學業<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.chroniclelive.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/edgar-man-u-target-1479505 |last=Oliver |first=Alan |date=4 January 2007 |accessdate=8 August 2014 |title=Edgar was a Man U target |newspaper=Evening Chronicle |location=Newcastle uon Tyne |archive-date=2019-06-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190612101707/https://www.chroniclelive.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/edgar-man-u-target-1479505 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。艾加在冰球亦有出色的表現，更被認為有潛質獲得選秀進入[[國家冰球聯盟|國家冰球聯盟]]<ref name="The Star">{{cite news |url=http://www.thestar.com/news/2007/01/02/canadian_an_english_soccer_hero.html |accessdate=8 August 2014 |title=Canadian an English soccer hero |last=Lai |first=Tim |newspaper=Toronto Star |date=2 January 2007 |archive-date=2021-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226210229/https://www.thestar.com/news/2007/01/02/canadian_an_english_soccer_hero.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。11歲起他便參加安大略省級足球比賽<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.fifa.com/tournaments/archive/u20worldcup/canada2007/news/newsid=541535/index.html |accessdate=8 August 2014 |date=30 June 2007 |title=Old pals hold Canuck hopes |publisher=FIFA |archive-date=2014-10-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141006160527/http://www.fifa.com/tournaments/archive/u20worldcup/canada2007/news/newsid=541535/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，之後他在足球和冰球之間徘徊，直到13歲那年決定放棄冰球，把時間放在足球上<ref name="The Star" />。14歲那年，他在多個球會試訓並表現出色<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.canada.com/nationalpost/news/sports/story.html?id=b4731ca2-678f-4ef6-8744-bc5f87380878 |date=6 January 2007 |accessdate=8 August 2014 |title=Magpie flying high |newspaper=National Post |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140601001146/http://www.canada.com/nationalpost/news/sports/story.html?id=b4731ca2-678f-4ef6-8744-bc5f87380878 |archivedate=2014年6月1日 }}</ref>，並獲得纽卡斯尔联學院提供的獎學金，埃德加接受了並離開加拿大前往英國，與在[[泰恩-威爾郡|泰恩-威爾郡]]的祖母同居。

=== 成年生涯 ===
;紐卡素
[[File:DavidEdgar_interview.JPG|thumb]]

2006/07球季季中，紐卡素因眾多傷員問題，在預備隊的埃德加被臨時抽調至一隊。他在2006年12月26日對[[博尔顿足球俱乐部|博尔顿]]賽事首次上場<ref name=sb0607>{{cite web |url=http://www.soccerbase.com/players/player.sd?player_id=45658&season_id=136 |title=Games played by David Edgar in 2006/2007 |website=Soccerbase |publisher=Centurycomm |accessdate=8 August 2014 |archive-date=2019-06-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190630095140/https://www.soccerbase.com/players/player.sd?player_id=45658&season_id=136 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，1月1日主場對[[曼聯|曼聯]]的比賽更打進首顆職業進球，最終以2-2迫和曼聯<ref>{{cite news|first=Saj|last=Chowdhury|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/6205747.stm|title=Newcastle 2–2 Man Utd|publisher=BBC Sport|date=1 January 2007|accessdate=1 January 2007|archive-date=2007-01-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070118233425/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/6205747.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由於一隊後防傷員眾多，埃德加在場上只能踢他不擅長的邊後衛。賽後他被評為賽事最佳球員並得到教練的[[格伦·罗德尔|格伦·罗德尔]]的讚揚，成功緊盯[[基斯坦奴·朗拿度|基斯坦奴·朗拿度]]<ref>{{cite news|first=Michael|last=Walker|url=http://www.theguardian.com/football/2007/jan/02/match.sport4|title=Edgar the unknown clips United's wings|newspaper=The Guardian|date=2 January 2007|accessdate=8 August 2014|location=London|archive-date=2019-06-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190629030612/https://www.theguardian.com/football/2007/jan/02/match.sport4|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|first=Alex|last=Dunn|url=http://www1.skysports.com/football/news/11678/2400929/roeder-praise-for-edgar|title=Roeder praise for Edgar|publisher=Sky Sports|date=1 January 2007|accessdate=8 August 2014|archive-date=2019-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190706210515/https://www.skysports.com/football/news/11678/2400929/roeder-praise-for-edgar|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

07/08球季的埃德加是預備隊隊長，但球季過了一半後仍未有一次一隊上場機會，之後他公開表示對自己缺乏一隊上場機會感到沮喪<ref>{{cite news |first=Graeme |last=Bailey |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11678_3161329,00.html |date=18 February 2008 |accessdate=8 August 2014 |title=Toon starlet unsettled |publisher=Sky Sports |archive-date=2016-08-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160815071723/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11678_3161329,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。季末他獲得五次上場機會，其中對[[雷丁足球俱乐部|雷丁]]的表現更獲得教練的稱讚<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/n/newcastle_united/7334337.stm |accessdate=7 April 2008 |title=Keegan hails Barton re-emergence |publisher=BBC Sport |date=7 April 2008 |archive-date=2008-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080411052359/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/n/newcastle_united/7334337.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。埃德加在2007年5月5日與球會續約兩年。他在2008年12月28日以5-1大敗[[利物浦足球俱乐部|利物浦]]賽事中打進一球<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/7788422.stm |title=Newcastle 1–5 Liverpool |publisher=BBC Sport |date=28 December 2008 |accessdate=24 October 2009 |first=Phil |last=McNulty |archive-date=2009-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090116074315/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/7788422.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2009年5月24日球季最後一場賽事對[[阿士東維拉足球會|阿士東維拉]]中，埃德加在完場前被逐離場並以1-0落敗。該球季埃德加的13次上場，球隊錄得11負2和的劣跡，球隊保級失敗。季後他拒絕了會方合約並離隊<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.chroniclelive.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/david-edgar-exits-newcastle-united-1456597 |title=David Edgar exits Newcastle United for Burnley |first=Lee |last=Ryder |newspaper=Chronicle |location=Newcastle upon Tyne |date=30 June 2009 |accessdate=8 August 2014 |archive-date=2018-06-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180618230342/https://www.chroniclelive.co.uk/sport/football/football-news/david-edgar-exits-newcastle-united-1456597 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=sb0809>{{cite web |url=http://www.soccerbase.com/players/player.sd?player_id=45658&season_id=138 |title=Games played by David Edgar in 2008/2009 |website=Soccerbase |publisher=Centurycomm |accessdate=8 August 2014 |archive-date=2016-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305020256/http://www.soccerbase.com/players/player.sd?player_id=45658&season_id=138 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

;般尼
2009年7月1日，[[伯恩利足球俱乐部|伯恩利]]宣佈簽下大卫·埃德加，簽約四年<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/b/burnley/8128950.stm|title=Burnley bring in defender Edgar|date=1 July 2009|publisher=BBC Sport|accessdate=1 July 2009|archive-date=2017-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170807115920/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/b/burnley/8128950.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。12月24日，球會宣佈與紐卡素在埃德加轉會費達成共識，為30萬英鎊<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/b/burnley/8429612.stm |title=Burnley settle on fee with Newcastle for David Edgar |date=24 December 2009 |accessdate=25 December 2009 |publisher=BBC Sport |archive-date=2017-08-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170807115619/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/b/burnley/8429612.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2009年8月25日[[英格蘭聯賽盃|英格蘭聯賽盃]]對[[哈特尔普尔联足球俱乐部|哈特尔普尔联]]，埃德加首次代表伯恩利上場<ref name=sb0910>{{cite web |url=http://www.soccerbase.com/players/player.sd?player_id=45658&season_id=139 |title=Games played by David Edgar in 2009/2010 |website=Soccerbase |publisher=Centurycomm |accessdate=8 August 2014 |archive-date=2019-06-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190621203034/https://www.soccerbase.com/players/player.sd?player_id=45658&season_id=139 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。然而他不受教練[[欧文·科尔|欧文·科尔]]器重，得不到比賽機會。新教練[[布莱恩·劳斯|布莱恩·劳斯]]執教首場賽事便把埃德加放進對曼聯的先發名單，但最終仍以3-0大敗<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/b/burnley/8454402.stm |title=Burnley appoint Brian Laws as new manager |date=13 January 2010 |accessdate=8 August 2014 |publisher=BBC Sport |archive-date=2010-01-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100113052628/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/b/burnley/8454402.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=sb0910/>。

;外借史雲斯
2010年3月，埃德加外借至[[斯旺西城足球俱乐部|斯旺西城]]<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/8583837.stm |title=Swansea City sign defender David Edgar from Burnley|publisher=BBC Sport|date=23 March 2010|accessdate=29 March 2010}}</ref>。4月5日對[[斯坎索普联足球俱乐部|斯坎索普联]]的賽事中打進在球會首顆進球，以3-0獲勝<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_1/8595494.stm |title=Swansea 3–0 Scunthorpe|publisher=BBC Sport|date=5 April 2010|accessdate=8 August 2014}}</ref>。效力斯旺西城期間共上場5次及1進球<ref name=sb0910/>。

2011年月1日31日，球會宣佈再次把埃德加外借到斯旺西城至季末<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/9383075.stm |title=Swansea City capture David Edgar loan signing |publisher=BBC Sport |date=1 February 2011 |accessdate=8 August 2014}}</ref>，但數週後[[国际足球联合会|FIFA]]以文件不齊為理由拒絕給予国际证明<ref>{{cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/s/swansea_city/9398851.stm |title=Swansea City loanee David Edgar returns to Burnley |publisher=BBC Sport |date=17 February 2011 |accessdate=8 August 2014}}</ref>。

;回歸般尼
11/12球季，埃德加成為了球會主力後衛，並在2011年11月26日作客[[赫尔城足球俱乐部|赫尔城]]賽事中四分鐘內打進2球，以3-2擊敗對手<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www1.skysports.com/football/live/match/238467/report |title=Clarets fightback stuns Tigers |date=26 November 2011 |accessdate=8 August 2014 |publisher=Sky Sports |archive-date=2014-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141025140651/http://www1.skysports.com/football/live/match/238467/report |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

13/14球季結束後，球隊將會晉級至英超聯，而埃德加亦球會合約亦完結並被釋出<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/27293148 |title=Burnley: David Edgar, Brian Stock & Keith Treacy released |date=6 May 2014 |accessdate=8 August 2014 |publisher=BBC Sport |archive-date=2016-01-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160116233633/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/27293148 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

;伯明翰城
2014年6月12日，埃德加以自由身轉投[[伯明翰足球會|伯明翰城]]並簽約兩年<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football-27809809 |title=Birmingham City: Wes Thomas and David Edgar sign for Blues |publisher=BBC Sport |date=12 June 2014 |accessdate=12 June 2014}}</ref>。首次上場是在聯賽揭幕日對[[米德尔斯堡足球俱乐部|米德尔斯堡]]<ref name=sb1415>{{cite web |url=http://www.soccerbase.com/players/player.sd?player_id=45658&season_id=144 |title=Games played by David Edgar in 2014/2015 |website=Soccerbase |publisher=Centurycomm |accessdate=22 October 2014 |archive-date=2019-06-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190621035156/https://www.soccerbase.com/players/player.sd?player_id=45658&season_id=144 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並在8月19日主場以2-2戰平[[伊普斯维奇城足球俱乐部|伊普斯维奇城]]賽事中攻入在球會首顆進球<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/28749922 |title=Birmingham 2–2 Ipswich |publisher=BBC Sport |date=19 August 2014 |accessdate=20 August 2014 |archive-date=2014-08-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140822024204/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/28749922 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

