=== 國家隊 ===
[[Image:David_edgar_vs._usa,_june_2012.jpg|thumb]]

埃德加曾代表[[加拿大17歲以下國家足球隊|加拿大U-17]]和[[加拿大20歲以下國家足球隊|加拿大U-20]]，16歲時便被徵召上參加[[2003年世界青年足球錦標賽|2003年世界青年足球錦標賽]]。

2007年2月1日，埃德加當選為2006球季加拿大最佳年青球員<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.canadasoccer.com/david-edgar-jodi-ann-robinson-named-canadian-youth-players-of-the-year-p147062 |date=1 February 2007 |title=David Edgar, Jodi-Ann Robinson named Canadian Youth Players of the Year |publisher=Canadian Soccer Association |accessdate=8 August 2014 |archive-date=2014-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140811095651/http://www.canadasoccer.com/david-edgar-jodi-ann-robinson-named-canadian-youth-players-of-the-year-p147062 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他在2007年入選了在加拿大主辦的[[2007年世界青年足球錦標賽|世界青年足球錦標賽]]參賽名單<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.canadasoccer.com/canada-s-u-20-world-cup-team-to-take-part-in-adidas-camp-p147043 |title=Canada's U-20 World Cup team to take part in adidas camp |accessdate=8 August 2014 |publisher=Canadian Soccer Association |date=15 March 2007 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141025185328/http://www.canadasoccer.com/canada-s-u-20-world-cup-team-to-take-part-in-adidas-camp-p147043 |archive-date=2014-10-25 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>，是加拿大有史以來主辦過最大型的單一體育項目賽事<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.canadasoccer.com/it-s-final-toronto-to-host-fifa-u-20-world-cup-championship-game-p147198 |title=Toronto to Host FIFA U-20 World Cup Championship Game |accessdate=8 August 2014 |publisher=Canadian Soccer Association |date=26 January 2006 |archive-date=2019-06-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190619172640/https://www.canadasoccer.com/it-s-final-toronto-to-host-fifa-u-20-world-cup-championship-game-p147198 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。埃德加在賽事開始前三星期受傷<ref>{{cite news |first=Richard |last=Starnes |url=http://www.canada.com/topics/sports/story.html?id=8ca028d7-2a75-4f2a-b080-ee91639c908d&k=48521 |title=Canada's captain sits out under-20 loss |accessdate=4 June 2007 |publisher=Canada.com |date=4 June 2007 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071208052636/http://www.canada.com/topics/sports/story.html?id=8ca028d7-2a75-4f2a-b080-ee91639c908d&k=48521 |archivedate=2007年12月8日 }}</ref>，使他上陣成疑。後來的[[核磁共振成像|核磁共振成像]]顯示沒有大礙，並參與了所有賽事共3場<ref name="Edmonton Journal">{{cite news |url=http://www.canada.com/edmontonjournal/news/sports/story.html?id=927444e6-416c-41b8-ac2a-7de944f3f7b1&p=1 |accessdate=8 August 2014 |title=Edgar still stuck in the bleachers |last=Petersen |first=Scott |newspaper=Edmonton Journal |date=15 June 2007 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140813212551/http://www.canada.com/edmontonjournal/news/sports/story.html?id=927444e6-416c-41b8-ac2a-7de944f3f7b1&p=1 |archivedate=2014年8月13日 }}</ref>。

埃德加在2008年11月入選成年國家隊，在[[2010年世界盃外圍賽|2010年世界盃外圍賽]]對[[牙買加國家足球隊|牙買加]]賽事中為未用替補<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/archive/southafrica2010/preliminaries/nccamerica/matches/round=250468/match=300053874/report.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131204042039/http://www.fifa.com/worldcup/archive/southafrica2010/preliminaries/nccamerica/matches/round=250468/match=300053874/report.html |title=2010 FIFA World Cup Preliminaries: North, Central America and Caribbean: Jamaica–Canada |publisher=FIFA |archivedate=2013-12-04 |access-date=2014-09-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

埃德加的國家隊處子戰是在2011年2月9日對希臘，在半場換入。該比賽亦有另外兩名隊員首秀，最終希臘以1-0獲勝<ref>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110927102949/http://www.canadasoccer.com/tourney/FIFA_WC/game_profile.asp?gameId=1870 |url=http://canadasoccer.com/tourney/FIFA_WC/game_profile.asp?gameId=1870 |title=9.2.2011 – CAN 0:1 GRE |publisher=Caadian Soccer Association |date=9 February 2011 |archivedate=2011-09-27 |access-date=2014-09-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

埃德加入選[[2011年美洲金盃|2011年美洲金盃]]參賽名單，以代替因傷退出的[[德扬·亚科维奇|德扬·亚科维奇]]<ref name="CBC">{{cite news |url=http://www.cbc.ca/sports/soccer/story/2011/06/06/sp-canada-us-gold-cup.html |accessdate=6 June 2011 |title=Canada set for Gold Cup showdown with USA |last=Molinaro |first=John F. |publisher=CBC Sports |date=6 June 2011 |archive-date=2011-08-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110806015211/http://www.cbc.ca/sports/soccer/story/2011/06/06/sp-canada-us-gold-cup.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，但國家隊在小組賽已被淘汰出局，因此埃德加未有上場機會。2011年底起，他成為了國家隊的主力球員，2012年10月12日的[[2014年世界盃外圍賽|2014年世界盃外圍賽]]對[[古巴國家足球隊|古巴]]的比賽更交出助攻和進球，使加拿大以3-0取勝<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.vancouversun.com/sports/Canada+tops+Cuba+qualifier/6756975/story.html |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120615215147/http://www.vancouversun.com/sports/Canada+tops+Cuba+qualifier/6756975/story.html |title=Canada tops Cuba in qualifier |newspaper=Vancouver Sun |date=9 June 2012 |archivedate=2012-06-15 |accessdate=2014-09-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此外他亦入選了[[2013年美洲金盃|2013年美洲金盃]]參賽名單<ref>{{Cite news |title=Canada Finalize roster for Gold Cup, announces friendly |url=http://www.canadasoccer.com/canada-finalizes-roster-for-gold-cup-announces-friendly--p154281 |publisher=Canadian Soccer Association |date=27 June 2013 |accessdate=29 June 2013 |archive-date=2019-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190328031432/https://www.canadasoccer.com/canada-finalizes-roster-for-gold-cup-announces-friendly--p154281 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

